                <table align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:100%; min-width:100%;" width="100%" class="mcnTextContentContainer">
                    <tbody><tr>
                        
                        <td valign="top" class="mcnTextContent" style="padding: 0px 18px 9px;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;">
                        
                            <div style="text-align: left;"><br>
<br>
<span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong><span style="color:#D3D3D3">6. 關於穿什麼，有哪些特別限制嗎？</span></strong></span></span></div>

<div style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</div>

<div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif"><span style="font-size:12px">可以穿著你喜歡的服裝前來，不過我們會建議穿平底鞋，畢竟需要在黑暗中走動還是安全點好。不過，為維持無光環境，<span style="color:#8C5FB4"><u><strong>請避免穿著會反光或閃閃動人的華麗服裝</strong></u></span>。<br>
<br>
除此之外，無光晚餐寄物空間有限，也沒有傳說中的無限黑洞，用餐前需將包包、⼤型⾐物（如厚重外套、手錶、手機、或任何會發光的物品）寄放於接待區，所以建議不要帶太多東西到訪。畢竟，旅途中的輕量化能讓你減少重力的影響。同時，為使⿊暗中體驗順暢，<span style="color:#8C5FB4"><u><strong>個人物品需全部寄物，無法攜帶進場。</strong></u></span><br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<span style="color:#D3D3D3"><strong>7. 發票可以打統編嗎？？</strong></span></span></span>

<div>&nbsp;</div>
<span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif"> <span style="font-size:12px"> 可以。若你在訂位時忘了備註，歡迎先來信說明（比如，現在回個信與我們說一聲），註記統編與抬頭，讓當天好好用餐，不被小事干擾。</span></span>

<div><br>
&nbsp;</div>
<br>
<span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="color:#D3D3D3"><strong>8. 黑暗中會發生意想不到的事嗎？</strong></span></span></span>

<div>&nbsp;</div>
<span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif"> <span style="font-size:12px"> 在黑暗中可能會遇到各種意料之外的事，如果遇到了，不妨開心接受他。例如：與鄰桌客人開始尬聊，結果發現你們都來自同一個星球。（開玩笑的）<br>
<br>
體驗時，若你或同行友人，出現幽閉恐懼等相關症狀，或因⿊暗嚇到吃⼿⼿、需要使⽤洗⼿間，可隨時向服務人員反應，將由服務人員引導出場休息。此外，考量到星際旅行時的安全以及效果，無光晚餐需年滿 16 歲以上方可體驗。</span></span>

<div>&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;"><br>
<span style="font-size:12px"><span style="color:#cccccc"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif"><strong>最後，貼心的小資訊，給即將到訪的你：</strong></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="color:#cccccc"><strong><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">無光晚餐鄰近停車場資訊｜</span></strong></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;"><u><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif"><strong>嘟嘟房（僑安站）</strong></span></span></u></p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">營業時間：24小時</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">地址：<a href="https://goo.gl/maps/HnGdPBN5HRGVaNRw7"><span style="color:#D3D3D3">106台北市大安區忠孝東路四段306號B1F</span></a></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;"><u><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif"><strong>CITY PARKING</strong></span></span></u></p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">營業時間：24小時</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;"><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">地址：<a href="https://goo.gl/maps/HjUpMEtxXuYrPw246"><span style="color:#D3D3D3">106台北市大安區仁愛路四段280號</span></a></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;"><span style="font-size:12px"><strong><span style="font-family:georgia,times,times new roman,serif">溫馨提醒：東區商圈車位較少，建議儘早前來尋找適合的車位，或搭乘大眾交通運輸，以避免遲到後無法入場體驗。</span></strong></span></p>

<p style="text-align: left;color: #A7A7A7;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, Baskerville, Georgia, serif;font-size: 13px;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;line-height: 200%;">&nbsp;</p>
